<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="decrease-v">decrease <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'kriːs/    美 /dɪ'kriːs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 减少；(使) 减小：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The number of new students <strong>decreased from</strong> 210 <strong>to</strong> 160 this year. 
今年新生的数量从210人减少到160人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The price of wheat <strong>decreased by</strong> 15% last year. 
去年小麦的价格下降了15%。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People planted trees on the waste hills to decrease water and soil loss. 
人们在荒丘上种植了树木，以减少水土流失。</p></div></div>